[package]
name = "beacn-lib"
version = "0.1.1"
edition = "2024"

[dependencies]
enum-map = "2.7.3"
byteorder = "1.5.0"
log = "0.4.26"
anyhow = "1.0.96"
rusb = "0.9.4"
crossbeam = "0.8.4"
jpeg-decoder = "0.3.1"
thiserror = "2.0.16"

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27.1"
features = [ "strum_macros", "derive",]

[[example]]
name = "async"
required-features = [ "tokio",]
doc-scrape-examples = true

[[example]]
name = "async_smol"
required-features = [ "async-io",]
doc-scrape-examples = false

[[example]]
name = "blocking"
required-features = [ "blocking",]
doc-scrape-examples = true

[[example]]
name = "custom_icon"
required-features = [ "tokio",]
doc-scrape-examples = true

[package]
name = "ksni"
version = "0.3.1"
authors = [ "iovxw <iovxw@outlook.com>",]
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.80"
description = "A Rust implementation of the KDE/freedesktop StatusNotifierItem specification\n"
repository = "https://github.com/iovxw/ksni"
keywords = [ "systray", "linux", "gui",]
categories = [ "api-bindings",]
license = "Unlicense"

[features]
default = [ "tokio",]
blocking = [ "dep:once_cell",]
tokio = [ "dep:tokio", "zbus/tokio",]
async-io = [ "dep:async-io", "dep:async-lock", "dep:async-executor", "dep:futures-lite", "dep:futures-channel", "dep:once_cell", "zbus/async-io",]

[dependencies]
paste = "1"
futures-util = "0.3"

[dev-dependencies]
smol = "2"
smol-macros = "0.1"
macro_rules_attribute = "0.2"
image = "0.25"

[dependencies.zbus]
version = "5"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1"
features = [ "rt", "macros",]
optional = true

[dependencies.async-io]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-lock]
version = "3"
optional = true

[dependencies.async-executor]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-lite]
version = "2"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-channel]
version = "0.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.once_cell]
version = "1"
optional = true

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
features = [ "blocking",]

[package]
name = "pipeweaver-ipc"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Craig McLure <craig@mclure.net>",]
repository = "https://github.com/pipeweaver/pipeweaver"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
anyhow = "1.0.95"
json-patch = "4.1.0"
async-trait = "0.1.86"
futures = "0.3.31"

[dependencies.pipeweaver-shared]
path = "../shared"

[dependencies.pipeweaver-profile]
path = "../profile"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.interprocess]
version = "2.2.1"
features = [ "tokio",]

[dependencies.ulid]
version = "1.2.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.enum-map]
version = "2.7.3"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7.13"
features = [ "codec", "compat",]

[dependencies.tokio-serde]
version = "0.9.0"
features = [ "bincode", "json",]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12.12"
default-features = false
features = [ "json",]

[package]
name = "pipeweaver-profile"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Craig McLure <craig@mclure.net>",]
repository = "https://github.com/pipeweaver/pipeweaver"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.138"
strum_macros = "0.27.0"

[dependencies.pipeweaver-shared]
path = "../shared"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.ulid]
version = "1.2.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.enum-map]
version = "2.7.3"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27.0"

[package]
name = "pipeweaver-shared"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2021"
authors = [ "Craig McLure <craig@mclure.net>",]
repository = "https://github.com/pipeweaver/pipeweaver"
license = "MIT"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.138"
strum_macros = "0.27.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.217"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.ulid]
version = "1.2.0"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.enum-map]
version = "2.7.3"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.strum]
version = "0.27.0"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/beacn-on-linux/beacn-lib"]
git = "https://github.com/beacn-on-linux/beacn-lib"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
tag = "v0.1.3"

[source."https://github.com/frostycoolslug/ksni"]
git = "https://github.com/frostycoolslug/ksni"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/pipeweaver/pipeweaver"]
git = "https://github.com/pipeweaver/pipeweaver"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
